16/11/2010
PRISTINA, Kosovo -- Over 200 NGOs made their co-operation official on Monday (November 15th) under the name "Coalition for Democracy".
Sejdi Demiri, a representative of the coalition, said that it will defend, respect and promote human rights and freedoms in Kosovo and beyond.
The Coalition for Democracy also announced that if it manages to raise funds, it will monitor the December 12th elections.
(TV 21, RTK - 15/11/10)
